  "linked_names": [],
  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "{upside-down} I was right, and the literal order of the universe is moral, my acting right would pay off -- and it did; they gave me Diana as my guide, my tutelary spirit.\n\n{rightside-up} Would there be any other way to correct the copy, whose degeneration is a form of entropy, than for the monitoring circuit to \"cut in\" and replace (and then change) the dis figured portions? He removes what is wrong, and introjects what is good that's lacking; it's a double processing of adding and subtracting,",
      "matched_alias": "Form World",
      "term_id": "TERM_form-world",
      "term_name": "Form World",
      "term_slug": "form-world"
    },
    {
      "text": "then \"tears\" carried a series of messages.\n\nKing Felix does identify Acts, but it says \"Christ returns at the reign of Felix.\" It says, \"Acts is now (the world of \"tears\") and the Second Advent is now occurring, at that time (c. AD 70) although it seems to us to be 1974.\" Then Valis-Zebra-Ubik is Christ returning as King leading the hosts (as depicted in the dream in \"tears\".) and the magician is told he will die, so judged by Christ the King. We are told, help has come and entered the prison. S",
      "matched_alias": "Jason Taverner",
      "term_id": "TERM_jason-taverner",
      "term_name": "Jason Taverner",
      "term_slug": "jason-taverner"
    }
  ],
